ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectContributions to assist livestock producers in British Columbia
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for FEDERAL CONTRIBUTIONS OF UP TO $120,000 TO ASSIST LIVESTOCK PRODUCERS in BRITISH COLUMBIA whose animals were quarantined following the discovery of BOVINE TUBERCULOSIS in a British Columbia cow.
